# Conclusion

The Smart Lender project workflow demonstrates a complete end-to-end machine learning lifecycle for loan approval prediction. Through systematic data preprocessing, multiple model evaluations, and Flask-based deployment, the project successfully delivers an intelligent web application capable of assisting financial institutions in making faster and more accurate loan approval decisions.
